Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 16:56:01 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 13/16] Show prompt-cycle usage on completed-turn markers

Carry aggregate PromptUsage on durable and legacy terminal rails and enrich the existing Worked-for marker with uncached input/output, TPS, cache reads/writes, hit ratio, context start:end, and trusted complete cost. Converge driver, viewer, and lost-RPC finalization while preserving legacy and nonstandard marker behavior.
